                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Evaluating 评价",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nA 2% minoxidil solution is used for topical treatment of baldness. The usual dosage is 1 mL applied twice a day. Options 1, 3, and 4 are incorrect.\n\nTest-Taking Strategy:\nFocus on the subject, frequency of application of this medication, and note the strategic word, effective. Knowledge regarding the usual dosage for minoxidil solution is required to answer this question. Remember that this medication is applied twice daily.\n\nClient Needs: Physiological Integrity\nClinical Judgment/Cognitive Skill(s): Evaluate Outcomes\nCognitive Ability: Evaluating\nContent Area: Pharmacology: Cardiovascular: Vasodilators\nIntegrated Process: Nursing Process/Evaluation\nPriority Concepts: Clinical Judgment, Patient Education\nStrategies: Strategic Words, Subject\n",
                        "id": "6d15e1ab7115453bba8063748970721c",
